snippet.title: Minigolf Party by Playfish
snippet.description:
Play at http://apps.facebook.com/minigolfparty - Get your golf on and join the fun with
Minigolf Party! This crazy collection of courses takes you on the minigolf ride of your life. Jump over water hazards, dodge dangerous monsters, find your own secret routes and go for that sensational hole in one feeling. Create your own minigolf avatar and challenge your friends.
